# 🏢 Saudi Establishments Dashboard 2023

Overview
This dashboard analyzes establishments in Saudi Arabia for 2023, focusing on distribution by size, region, and quarterly trends.

Objective
To provide clear insights into establishment distribution to support planning and decision-making.

Key Insights
Total establishments reached 1.31M.
Micro establishments represent the majority with 1.14M.
Small establishments reached 150K, while medium establishments were 18.67K.
Large establishments totaled 3,885.
Riyadh is the top region by number of establishments.
The fourth quarter recorded the highest activity.

Tools Used
Power BI
Excel


